Package fr.upmc.datacenter.hardware.computers.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ComputerDynamicStateI
    The interface ComputerDynamicStateI implements objects representing the dynamic state information of computers transmitted through the ComputerDynamicStateDataI interface of Computer components.
    ComputerServicesI
    The interface ComputerServicesI defines the services offered by Computer>/code> components (allocating cores).
    ComputerStateDataConsumerI
    The interface ComputerStateDataConsumerI defines the consumer side methods used to receive state data pushed by a computer, both static and dynamic.
    ComputerStaticStateDataI
    The interface ComputerStaticStateDataI defines the static state notification services for Computer components.
    ComputerStaticStateI
    The class ComputerStaticStateI implements objects representing the static state information of computers transmitted through the ComputerStaticStateDataI interface of Computer components.
